 and explicit\ndefinitions if they exist and turn the complexity upper bound proof into an\nalgorithm computing them, at least for description logics with role inclusions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2020 13:16:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Aug 2020 08:52:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 28 Dec 2020 11:48:02 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 17 Aug 2022 15:49:55 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 28 Apr 2023 13:27:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-01"}
