ccurs in certain scenarios\neven if trait 2 (which benefits from transfer at the cost of trait 1) would be\nunfit when being merely on its own. In the case of founder control, the\nlimiting dynamical system has an unstable coexistence equilibrium. In all\ncases, we observe the classical (up to 3) phases of invasion dynamics \\`a la\nChampagnat (2006).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2020 15:08:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Aug 2020 07:58:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2020 14:49:18 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 25 May 2021 17:07:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-26"}
